&lt;p&gt;My abstract design is inspired by a &lt;a href=&#34;https://media.disneyanimation.com/uploads/production/publication_asset/140/asset/BH6_Into_the_Portal.pdf&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;talk at SIGGRAPH 2015 &amp;ndash; Big Hero 6: Into the Portal&lt;/a&gt;. 
They author this portal using a variation of Mandelbrot fractals with volumetric path tracing.
I went in another direction instead by applying deformers to geometry.&lt;/p&gt;






  



  
  











